+Ownership is especially important on distributed teams. Remote onboarding research from Microsoft found that new hires struggled with asking for help and building team connection when the communication path was unclear. A doc that lists the team lead, onboarding buddy, technical mentor, and preferred help channel solves a social problem, not just an informational one.
 
